value.0: You should... go tell your stories to Karlat... like Quint should have... Otherwise you'll bring change...
You should be talking to the Jharegs. I can't say any more. People talk too much, tell too many stories... Like that Quint.
There isn't much to say. We're a small village. We've two Lords, the Jharegs... Very normal, all around.
Perhaps you'd be better served by camping along the Neverwinter trade route... there's a new outpost... Highcliff... ?
Uh... sorry... please, you should speak with the Lords. It's not my business to discuss this.
Quint. Quint was his name. Always reading to the children! That leads to trouble. Please, I can't speak of this. Karlat will help you.
Have you heard about the plague in Neverwinter?
